-			7:00	-	ICT	1912 May
-			8:00	-	ICT	1931 May
+Zone Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh	7:06:40 -	LMT	1906 Jul  1
+			7:06:30	-	PLMT	1911 May  1
+			7:00	-	ICT	1942 Dec 31 23:00
+			8:00	-	IDT	1945 Mar 14 23:00
+			9:00	-	JST	1945 Sep  2
+			7:00	-	ICT	1947 Apr  1
+			8:00	-	IDT	1955 Jul  1
+			7:00	-	ICT	1959 Dec 31 23:00
+			8:00	-	IDT	1975 Jun 13
